# Verify Report — Password-Strength Meter (P4)

**Final status:** pass · **Criteria:** 14/14 met · **Blocking:** none · **Degraded:** no · **Regressions:** none open · **Micro-cycles:** 2 (cap 3)

Behavioral verification against the running page (local static server, headless Chromium probes + HTTP/CLI), skeptical-by-default. Initial run found real defects; two micro-cycles fixed them and re-probes confirmed green.

