## Defects found & fixed (micro-cycle history)

**Micro-cycle 1 (5 fixes):**
- **F9 / HIGH:** footer caveat claimed "Meeting every rule earns a Strong rating" — factually false (Strong needs length ≥ 12). Reworded accurately.
- **F6 / MEDIUM:** the `role=status` live region had no `sr-only` class → its text rendered visibly, duplicating the label. Made screen-reader-only.
- **F7 / floor:** rule-icon circles were empty → met/unmet conveyed by color alone for sighted users. Added visible ✓ / ✗ glyphs (`::before`).
- **LOW:** show/hide toggle didn't reset when the field was cleared. Added reset-on-empty.
- **AC5:** the spec internally contradicted itself (AC5 `''`→Weak vs plan-U4's blank-on-empty). The scorer correctly returns Weak for `''`; resolved toward the approved spec — the UI now reflects the scorer for all inputs (drop blank special-case).

**Micro-cycle 2 (2 fixes):**
- **F8 / floor (caught by the more rigorous re-probe; the first run mis-estimated it):** the Fair color `#b7710d` computes to only **3.90:1** on white at 14.4px bold — fails WCAG-AA 4.5:1. Changed to `#b45309` (**5.02:1**, passes). The floor (AA contrast) overrode the specific hex AC7 inherited from research. Weak `#c0392b` (5.44:1) and Strong `#1a7a3c` (5.39:1) already passed.
- **Regression (MEDIUM):** the AC5 fix made initial load (blank) diverge from post-clear ("Weak"). Unified: the empty "Weak" state now renders on load too, seeding `lastTier` so the live region stays silent on load and announces only on subsequent tier changes.

## Product decision recorded (for REVIEW)

- **Empty-input state shows "Weak"** (on initial load and after clearing), per the approved spec AC5 (`''`→Weak) and for consistency. The alternative — a neutral/blank empty state — is also reasonable UX; flagging it here so it can be revisited at REVIEW/SHIP if preferred.

## Accepted (won't-fix)

- **No `maxlength` on the input** (LOW): intentionally omitted — a hard cap could truncate valid long passphrases; client-side regex on each keystroke is sub-millisecond. Out of scope.

## Floors honored in the running app

F1 (no deps/build/CDN), F2 (no network/storage/console of the value), F3 (relative paths), F4 (root `index.html`), F5 (labelled input), F6 (sr-only live region, polite, atomic, tier-change-only, never assertive, silent on load), F7 (✓/✗ glyphs + text, not color alone), F8 (all tier text ≥ 4.5:1 AA), F9 (accurate non-overclaiming copy), F10 (`node --test`), F11 (single `scorer.js` source of truth), F12 ("password" in HTML).
